oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Group portrait of the Woodbury Bar Association. Seated in the first row are, from left to right, Arsolem Finley, James Jones, Captain J. St. John, A. J. Smithson, and Judge William Cannon Houston. Standing are Charles M. Preston, Sterling S. Brown, Walter Hancock, W. Mingle, and Judge John W. Preston.
